name: Bodyel - The Dancer
description:
Music: Analog synth and groovebox recording.
Artwork: Mixed media using brush tip marker and digital animation - 2021 - gif - 452x640 - Aline Vieira @floresfeias - Part of Codex Crypto Angelus series.

Bodyel is a dancer moving in magnetic waves and algorithmic gestures. 


Ethereal wing body and crypto gestures bring glory to the hands that trigger your shape with every click and typed command. Bless to the ones who dance in the spirit of Bodyel.
